Package org.ejbca.core.model.services

Interface IWorker

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseWorker, CertificateExpirationNotifierWorker, CRLDownloadWorker, CRLUpdateWorker, EmailSendingWorker, HsmKeepAliveWorker, PublishQueueProcessWorker, RenewCAWorker, RolloverWorker, UserPasswordExpireWorker
    public interface IWorker
    The worker interface of a service. It is the main class of a service. A worker has one IInterval and one IAction. The methods work() method is used to signal to this service that it is time to work.
    Version:
    $Id: IWorker.java 22117 2015-10-29 10:53:42Z mikekushner $
